(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Matt Maley, Equity Strategist at Miller Tabak, with a macro look at the equity markets and monetary policy. Broadcasting live from the Boston Convention and Exhibition Center.
